OL,3,CEx-pupils affected by infected blood
OL,4,Cscandal 'determined' to see
OL,5,Caccountability
OL,7,FFormer pupils of a boarding school in
OL,8,FHampshire who received medical
OL,9,Ftreatments using contaminated blood
OL,10,Fproducts in the 1970s and 1980s are
OL,11,F'determined' to hold the school to
OL,12,Faccount, part of their legal team has
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FSeveral former pupils of the Lord
OL,16,FMayor Treloar School and College,
OL,17,Fwhich at the time was a boarding
OL,18,Fschool for children with haemophilia,
OL,19,Fwant to take legal action against the
OL,20,FTreloar Trust, which operates the site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
