OL,7,FThey are seeking compensation over
OL,8,Fclaims that the school gave them
OL,9,Funlawful treatments involving
OL,10,Fcontaminated blood products, which
OL,11,Finfected them with a variety of
OL,12,Fdiseases including HIV and Hepatitis
OL,13,FA, B and C, without their or their
OL,14,Fparents' knowledge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
