OL,4,Cscandal 'determined' to see
OL,5,Caccountability
OL,7,FAt a hearing last month, lawyers for
OL,8,Fthe former pupils and their relatives
OL,9,Fsaid the cases should be managed
OL,10,Ftogether, while lawyers for the trust
OL,11,Fsaid the best way for the former
OL,12,Fpupils to be compensated will be
OL,13,Fthrough the Government's Infected
OL,14,FBlood Compensation Scheme.
OL,16,FAnd in a judgment on Tuesday, Judge
OL,17,FDavid Cook declined to make an order
OL,18,Fto manage the claims together, known
OL,19,Fas a group litigation order, finding
OL,20,Fthat those affected are not a
OL,21,F'homogeneous group'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
