OL,3,CEx-pupils affected by infected blood
OL,4,Cscandal 'determined' to see
OL,5,Caccountability
OL,7,FHe continued: "It is important that it
OL,8,Fshould be understood this does not
OL,9,Fmean the court is preventing these
OL,10,Fpotential claims from being progressed
OL,11,For is indicating any view upon the
OL,12,Fmerits of the potential claims.
OL,14,F"In the event that any of the
OL,15,Findividual claimants wish to issue a
OL,16,Fclaim, there is absolutely nothing to
OL,17,Fprevent them from doing so."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
