OL,7,FJudge Cook added that if multiple
OL,8,Fclaims were brought by 63 potential
OL,9,Fclaimants, their cases could be
OL,10,Fconsolidated.
OL,12,FHe added: "I am, however, far from
OL,13,Fsatisfied that 63 claims will
OL,14,Fmaterialise having regard to the
OL,15,Fimminent approval and implementation
OL,16,Fof the Infected Blood Compensation
OL,17,FScheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
