OL,7,F"In the event that any potential
OL,8,Fclaimant were to be able to make out a
OL,9,Fcase that they had not received proper
OL,10,Fcompensation, such claims could
OL,11,Fproceed efficiently and
OL,12,Fproportionately under court's ordinary
OL,13,Fpowers of case management."
OL,15,FFollowing the ruling, Des Collins, a
OL,16,Flegal adviser to the claimants, said
OL,17,Fthey were 'surprised and disappointed'
OL,18,Fby Tuesday's judgment, which they
OL,19,Fintend to appeal against.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
