OL,7,FMr Collins added: "It cannot be right
OL,8,Fthat the treatment of former pupils as
OL,9,Fguinea pigs by Treloar's in the 70s
OL,10,Fand 80s goes without sanction.
OL,12,F"Treloar's should not breathe a sigh
OL,13,Fof relief just yet since my clients
OL,14,Fremain determined to hold the school
OL,15,Fto account for the wrongs of the past."
