OL,7,FAt last month's hearing, barristers
OL,8,Ffor the trust apologised to former
OL,9,Fpupils in attendance, stating it was
OL,10,F'acutely aware of the pain and
OL,11,Fsuffering and the loss' they had
OL,12,Fendured.
OL,14,FReading a statement on the trust's
OL,15,Fbehalf, Toby Riley-Smith KC said it
OL,16,Fwas 'so sorry' that many former pupils
OL,17,F"were among those infected with
OL,18,Fhepatitis and HIV, as a result of
OL,19,Ftreatment with contaminated blood
OL,20,Fproducts".
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@IO]
