OL,7,FHe said: "It is so sorry that as a
OL,8,Fresult, they and their loved ones have
OL,9,Fsuffered so much, and for so long.
OL,11,F"It is so sorry that they have been
OL,12,Fvictims of this tragedy, which Sir
OL,13,FBrian Langstaff has described as the
OL,14,Fworst treatment disaster in the
OL,15,Fhistory of the NHS, a tragedy that has
OL,16,Fbeen compounded by the fact that it
OL,17,Fhas taken so long for their plight to
OL,18,Fbe recognised."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
