OL,7,FAfter the judgment, a spokesperson for
OL,8,FTreloar's said: "After careful
OL,9,Fconsideration of the evidence, the
OL,10,Fjudge has decided not to make a GLO.
OL,12,F"We firmly believe that the best route
OL,13,Ffor our former students to receive
OL,14,Ftimely and substantial recompense is
OL,15,Fvia the Government compensation scheme.
OL,17,F"We urge the Infected Blood
OL,18,FCompensation Authority to pay the
OL,19,Flevels of compensation that have
OL,20,Falready been set as soon as possible."
